And just mix the masa
harina with-- if you're

00:20:46.800 --> 00:20:49.130
making like a kilo
of masa harina,

00:20:49.130 --> 00:20:52.440
just have a bolito
like that, of my size,

00:20:52.440 --> 00:20:55.290
not yours-- you know, like this.

00:20:55.290 --> 00:20:59.540
50 grams of wheat flour.

00:20:59.540 --> 00:21:05.510
Mix it there, and add warm
water, tepid water that you

00:21:05.510 --> 00:21:11.820
can put your little
finger, and count until 10,

00:21:11.820 --> 00:21:13.240
without burning yourself.

00:21:13.240 --> 00:21:15.520
Don't go, one, two,
three, four, five, aah!

00:21:15.520 --> 00:21:16.060
No.

00:21:16.060 --> 00:21:18.580
Just warm water.

00:21:18.580 --> 00:21:19.830
And mix it.

00:21:19.830 --> 00:21:21.880
Enough water.

00:21:21.880 --> 00:21:25.620
And it has to be a little
bit sticky at the end,

00:21:25.620 --> 00:21:27.700
but then it's perfect.

00:21:27.700 --> 00:21:33.810
And you just make the little
bolitas, put them in the press.

00:21:33.810 --> 00:21:42.560
And the flat pan, the comal,
has to be thick and very hot,

00:21:42.560 --> 00:21:47.770
hot enough to seal the
tortilla right away.

00:21:47.770 --> 00:21:49.820
But as you don't
have any practice,

00:21:49.820 --> 00:21:51.490
and you will burn
your fingers if you

00:21:51.490 --> 00:21:58.760
try to turn the tortilla,
have one of those spatulas,

00:21:58.760 --> 00:21:59.470
and turn it.

00:21:59.470 --> 00:22:00.440
And that's it.

